Qatar Plans to Set Up U.S.-Based Islamic Fund, Al-Sharq Reports

-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 
2011-03-22T06:49:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/qatar-plans-to-set-up-u-s-based-islamic-fund-al-sharq-reports.html
Qatar plans to announce the
creation of an Islamic fund in the U.S. at an investment
conference in  New York  next month,  Al-Sharq reported , citing
Khalid Bin Thani Al Thani, vice president of the Qatari
Businessmen Association.  To contact the reporter on this story:
